Talk to Garnyd at Anazârmekhem in the Flaming Deeps of Moria

Garnyd salutes you.

'Well met, Captain. I see my summons for you was well-placed, as is the prevailing opinion of your value to our cause against the Enemy.

'I would have your aid here in our fight to reclaim Moria. Please stay a while and let us speak of how you can aid the cause.'
Captain Garnyd has summoned you into her presence.
Captain Garnyd has summoned you into her presence to further your training as a Captain.
